@{
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_PublicLayout.cshtml";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    ViewData["MetaDescription"] = "Read our Privacy Policy to understand how KSP Care collects, uses, and protects your personal and diagnostic information.";
}

@section Styles {
    <style>
        .policy-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .policy-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 20%;
            right: 20%;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(59,130,246,0.3), transparent);
        }
        @@media (min-width: 768px) { .policy-card { padding: 48px 56px; } }

        .policy-card h3 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .policy-card h3 .section-num {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: rgba(59,130,246,0.8);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .policy-card p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .policy-card ul {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            padding-left: 0;
            list-style: none;
        }
        .policy-card li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            padding-left: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .policy-card li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 10px;
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(59,130,246,0.4);
        }
        .policy-card strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
    </style>
}

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="mb-12 border-b border-white/[0.06] pb-10 anim-fade-up">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500/8 border border-blue-500/15 mb-6">
        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock text-blue-400 text-xs"></i>
        <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-blue-400/80 uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Legal</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
        <i class="bi bi-calendar3 text-xs"></i> Last Updated: March 2026
    </p>
</div>

<div class="policy-card anim-fade-up-delay-1">
    <p>At <strong>kspcare</strong>, your privacy and the security of your medical data are our highest priorities. This Privacy Policy explains how our Laboratory Information Management System (LIMS) collects, uses, protects, and handles your personal and diagnostic information.</p>

    <h3><span class="section-num">1</span> Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>To provide you with accurate diagnostic services and access to the Patient Portal, we collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Identification:</strong> First Name, Last Name, Age, Gender, and Mobile Number.</li>
        <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Ward Allocation, Area/Landmark, City, State, Country, and Pincode for home sample collection.</li>
        <li><strong>Medical & Diagnostic Data:</strong> Test results, pathology reports, and historical diagnostic data generated by our laboratory.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3><span class="section-num">2</span> How We Use Your Data</h3>
    <p>Your data is strictly used for healthcare and operational purposes, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Scheduling and executing home sample collections in the Manipal and Udupi regions.</li>
        <li>Processing diagnostic tests and generating accurate pathology reports.</li>
        <li>Synchronizing your data securely with our Staff Terminal for clinical review.</li>
        <li>Providing you with secure access to your historical records via the Patient Portal.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3><span class="section-num">3</span> Data Security & Encryption</h3>
    <p>We implement state-of-the-art security measures to ensure your data is protected against unauthorized access. All data transmitted between your browser and our LIMS servers is encrypted using standard cryptographic protocols. Access to your diagnostic data is restricted strictly to authorized clinical personnel and yourself.</p>

    <h3><span class="section-num">4</span> Data Sharing & Third Parties</h3>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal or medical information to external marketing agencies or third parties. We may only disclose your information when required by law or to trusted healthcare partners strictly involved in processing your specific diagnostic tests.</p>

    <h3><span class="section-num">5</span> Your Rights</h3>
    <p>You have the right to access, review, and request corrections to your personal information stored in our system. You may exercise these rights by accessing your Patient Portal or contacting our support team.</p>

    <h3><span class="section-num">6</span> Contact Us</h3>
    <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact our Data Protection Officer at:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@kspcare.com<br>
       <strong>Phone:</strong> +91 98765 43210</p>
</div>